				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Reilna is not online. Last active: 8/22/2004 8:44:27 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Reilna">Reilna</a><br></td>
