				<td colspan="2"><span>For AA grinding, I usually either swarm kite gargs in PoN or mobs in PoJ exec trial.  Gargs drops some decent gems and such that sell well at merchant.  As for PoJ trials, sometimes you get a nemd up which drops some decent items you can sell in bazaar.  The exp is about 1-2% AA per kill.
<br />

<br />
I have tried HoH chant kiting for abit but found the kite takes too long (however, I always look forward to them sentries.  hehe.)
