<br />

<br />
&lt;1&gt; Pull ALL the golems from west wall.
<br />

<br />
&lt;2&gt; Run to east wall and be careful not to lose your mobs.
<br />

<br />
&lt;3&gt; Collect ALL the golems from east wall.
<br />

<br />
&lt;4&gt; Pull the to the point at the wall by EW where there is a small flat area, and DA when the swarm of mobs catches up to you.
<br />

<br />
&lt;5&gt; In the ten seconds before you splat, turn OFF run and initiate your circles, doing it this way will ensure your circles are such that you wont run into the walls trying to get them right.
<br />

<br />
&lt;6&gt; Once your DA wears off they should be following you closely enough for even your close-range aes to hit without them hitting you. &lt;This is with selos and epic/IM3&gt;
<br />

<br />
&lt;7&gt; Recommended lineup for this is Marr, 4 AE Dots, Single-target snare &lt;they run when almost dead&gt;, DA, and Selos.
<br />

<br />
&lt;8&gt; THE LUTE!! Get a good one, the one bought from EC is one of the best, dont be too proud to spend hard-earned points on a 2.6 mod instrument.
<br />

<br />
Happy hunting!!</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%">Impresario Amedaius Bladewhisper, 70 ladies' broken hearts and 290 aa meetings. http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=851398</span></td>
