				<td colspan="2"><span>All golems and spiders you can get(I'd leave some for others if they have an established camp), run off(leved) EW cliff over the river...grab the 3 undead there(mez off any named), wait...golems and spiders should come down now head to the middle most undead house then back to the castle, mez off any undead doorman that adds, fade, reaggro pack.  Run along bank to the undead house there(no named in this one) get the skellies in the field and if the big horse guy is up target him immidiately and dont change.  Next, grab the 3 from footman house, an undead doorman can spawn here too, target him also.  Get your pack nice and tight, toggle back to horse man and highsun him then toggle to doorman and highsun him, FADE immidiately and reaggro pack.  Kite.  Frogs are good too, no crawlers like was mentioned also.</span></td>
